{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1261,"text":"I want you to imagine"},{"time":2753,"text":"what a breakthrough this was"},{"time":4708,"text":"for women who were victims of violence"},{"time":7136,"text":"in the 1980s."},{"time":9092,"text":"They would come into the emergency room"},{"time":12605,"text":"with what the police would call \"a lovers' quarrel,\""},{"time":16017,"text":"and I would see a woman who was beaten,"},{"time":19792,"text":"I would see a broken nose and a fractured wrist"},{"time":24534,"text":"and swollen eyes."},{"time":26295,"text":"And as activists, we would take our Polaroid camera,"},{"time":30333,"text":"we would take her picture,"},{"time":32890,"text":"we would wait 90 seconds,"},{"time":35042,"text":"and we would give her the photograph."},{"time":38169,"text":"And she would then have"},{"time":40063,"text":"the evidence she needed to go to court."},{"time":43290,"text":"We were making what was invisible visible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47724,"text":"I've been doing this for 30 years."},{"time":49695,"text":"I've been part of a social movement"},{"time":51858,"text":"that has been working on ending"},{"time":53821,"text":"violence against women and children."},{"time":57928,"text":"And for all those years,"},{"time":60817,"text":"I've had an absolutely passionate"},{"time":65549,"text":"and sometimes not popular belief"},{"time":68496,"text":"that this violence is not inevitable,"},{"time":71790,"text":"that it is learned, and if it's learned,"},{"time":74795,"text":"it can be un-learned, and it can be prevented."},{"time":78860,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86045,"text":"Why do I believe this?"},{"time":88008,"text":"Because it's true."},{"time":90221,"text":"It is absolutely true."},{"time":92458,"text":"Between 1993 and 2010,"},{"time":98014,"text":"domestic violence among adult women"},{"time":101347,"text":"in the United States"},{"time":102699,"text":"has gone down by 64 percent,"},{"time":106086,"text":"and that is great news."},{"time":108763,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111512,"text":"Sixty-four percent. Now, how did we get there?"},{"time":114615,"text":"Our eyes were wide open."},{"time":116410,"text":"Thirty years ago, women were beaten,"},{"time":118830,"text":"they were stalked, they were raped,"},{"time":120965,"text":"and no one talked about it."},{"time":123506,"text":"There was no justice."},{"time":125289,"text":"And as an activist, that was not good enough."},{"time":129913,"text":"And so step one on this journey"},{"time":132384,"text":"is we organized,"},{"time":134381,"text":"and we created this extraordinary"},{"time":137015,"text":"underground network of amazing women"},{"time":140007,"text":"who opened shelters,"},{"time":141874,"text":"and if they didn't open a shelter,"},{"time":143993,"text":"they opened their home"},{"time":145585,"text":"so that women and children could be safe."},{"time":148619,"text":"And you know what else we did?"},{"time":150299,"text":"We had bake sales, we had car washes,"},{"time":153764,"text":"and we did everything we could do to fundraise,"},{"time":156298,"text":"and then at one point we said,"},{"time":158275,"text":"you know, it's time that we went"},{"time":160416,"text":"to the federal government"},{"time":162070,"text":"and asked them to pay for these"},{"time":164041,"text":"extraordinary services that are saving people's lives."},{"time":168056,"text":"Right? (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":170517,"text":"And so, step number two,"},{"time":173591,"text":"we knew we needed to change the laws."},{"time":175936,"text":"And so we went to Washington,"},{"time":178223,"text":"and we lobbied for the first piece of legislation."},{"time":183093,"text":"And I remember walking through the halls"},{"time":185854,"text":"of the U.S. Capitol,"},{"time":188264,"text":"and I was in my 30s, and my life had purpose,"},{"time":192622,"text":"and I couldn't imagine"},{"time":194728,"text":"that anybody would ever challenge"},{"time":196855,"text":"this important piece of legislation."},{"time":198966,"text":"I was probably 30 and naive."},{"time":201902,"text":"But I heard about a congressman"},{"time":203984,"text":"who had a very, very different point of view."},{"time":206301,"text":"Do you know what he called"},{"time":208100,"text":"this important piece of legislation?"},{"time":210851,"text":"He called it the Take the Fun Out of Marriage Act."},{"time":214338,"text":"The Take the Fun Out of Marriage Act."},{"time":216517,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, that was in 1984"},{"time":218980,"text":"in the United States, and I wish I had Twitter."},{"time":222056,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":225243,"text":"Ten years later, after lots of hard work,"},{"time":228655,"text":"we finally passed the Violence Against Women Act,"},{"time":231732,"text":"which is a life-changing act"},{"time":233988,"text":"that has saved so many lives. (Applause)"},{"time":236842,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":238272,"text":"I was proud to be part of that work,"},{"time":241163,"text":"and it changed the laws"},{"time":243613,"text":"and it put millions of dollars into local communities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246464,"text":"And you know what else it did? It collected data."},{"time":248791,"text":"And I have to tell you, I'm passionate about data."},{"time":251474,"text":"In fact, I am a data nerd."},{"time":254056,"text":"I'm sure there are a lot of data nerds here."},{"time":256084,"text":"I am a data nerd,"},{"time":257429,"text":"and the reason for that is I want to make sure"},{"time":260064,"text":"that if we spend a dollar, that the program works,"},{"time":263510,"text":"and if it doesn't work, we should change the plan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267974,"text":"And I also want to say one other thing:"},{"time":271573,"text":"We are not going to solve this problem"},{"time":273788,"text":"by building more jails"},{"time":276641,"text":"or by even building more shelters."},{"time":278938,"text":"It is about economic empowerment for women,"},{"time":282131,"text":"it is about healing kids who are hurt,"},{"time":284876,"text":"and it is about prevention with a capital P."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288336,"text":"And so, step number three on this journey:"},{"time":292730,"text":"We know, if we're going to\nkeep making this progress,"},{"time":295682,"text":"we're going to have to turn up the volume,"},{"time":297983,"text":"we're going to have to increase the visibility,"},{"time":300195,"text":"and we're going to have to engage the public."},{"time":303107,"text":"And so knowing that, we went\nto the Advertising Council,"},{"time":306517,"text":"and we asked them to help us"},{"time":308838,"text":"build a public education campaign."},{"time":311428,"text":"And we looked around the world to Canada"},{"time":313884,"text":"and Australia and Brazil and parts of Africa,"},{"time":316526,"text":"and we took this knowledge"},{"time":318288,"text":"and we built the first national"},{"time":320781,"text":"public education campaign"},{"time":322872,"text":"called There's No Excuse for Domestic Violence."},{"time":325442,"text":"Take a look at one of our spots."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327641,"text":"(Video) Man: Where's dinner?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":329502,"text":"Woman: Well, I thought you'd be home a couple hours ago, and I put everything away, so—"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333014,"text":"Man: What is this? Pizza.\nWoman: If you had just called me,\nI would have known—"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336058,"text":"Man: Dinner? Dinner ready is a pizza?\nWoman: Honey, please don't be so loud."},{"time":339231,"text":"Please don't—Let go of me!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341136,"text":"Man: Get in the kitchen!\nWoman: No! Help!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":344030,"text":"Man: You want to see what hurts? (Slaps woman)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":346385,"text":"That's what hurts! That's what hurts!\n(Breaking glass)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":349803,"text":"Woman: Help me!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352044,"text":"[\"Children have to sit by and watch.\nWhat's your excuse?\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":355463,"text":"Esta Soler: As we were in the process"},{"time":357482,"text":"of releasing this campaign,"},{"time":359144,"text":"O.J. Simpson was arrested"},{"time":361327,"text":"for the murder of his wife and her friend."},{"time":365461,"text":"We learned that he had a long history"},{"time":367564,"text":"of domestic violence."},{"time":368937,"text":"The media became fixated."},{"time":371463,"text":"The story of domestic violence"},{"time":373482,"text":"went from the back page,"},{"time":374836,"text":"but actually from the no-page, to the front page."},{"time":377642,"text":"Our ads blanketed the airwaves,"},{"time":380596,"text":"and women, for the first time,"},{"time":382946,"text":"started to tell their stories."},{"time":385067,"text":"Movements are about moments,"},{"time":388420,"text":"and we seized this moment."},{"time":391014,"text":"And let me just put this in context."},{"time":393353,"text":"Before 1980, do you have any idea"},{"time":396489,"text":"how many articles were in The New York Times"},{"time":399774,"text":"on domestic violence?"},{"time":402787,"text":"I'll tell you: 158."},{"time":406451,"text":"And in the 2000s, over 7,000."},{"time":410962,"text":"We were obviously making a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413997,"text":"But we were still missing a critical element."},{"time":416743,"text":"So, step four: We needed to engage men."},{"time":422258,"text":"We couldn't solve this problem"},{"time":424201,"text":"with 50 percent of the population on the sidelines."},{"time":427318,"text":"And I already told you I'm a data nerd."},{"time":429538,"text":"National polling told us that men felt indicted"},{"time":433161,"text":"and not invited into this conversation."},{"time":435660,"text":"So we wondered, how can we include men?"},{"time":439376,"text":"How can we get men to talk about"},{"time":441495,"text":"violence against women and girls?"},{"time":444239,"text":"And a male friend of mine pulled me aside"},{"time":446893,"text":"and he said, \"You want men to talk about violence"},{"time":450269,"text":"against women and girls. Men don't talk.\""},{"time":453186,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":454902,"text":"I apologize to the men in the audience."},{"time":457178,"text":"I know you do."},{"time":458652,"text":"But he said, \"Do you know what they do do?"},{"time":460706,"text":"They do talk to their kids."},{"time":462385,"text":"They talk to their kids as parents, as coaches.\""},{"time":465902,"text":"And that's what we did."},{"time":467546,"text":"We met men where they were at"},{"time":469320,"text":"and we built a program."},{"time":470859,"text":"And then we had this one event"},{"time":472638,"text":"that stays in my heart forever"},{"time":474713,"text":"where a basketball coach"},{"time":477298,"text":"was talking to a room filled with male athletes"},{"time":481220,"text":"and men from all walks of life."},{"time":483801,"text":"And he was talking about the importance"},{"time":485704,"text":"of coaching boys into men"},{"time":487063,"text":"and changing the culture of the locker room"},{"time":489101,"text":"and giving men the tools to\nhave healthy relationships."},{"time":492370,"text":"And all of a sudden, he looked\nat the back of the room,"},{"time":495298,"text":"and he saw his daughter,"},{"time":497010,"text":"and he called out his daughter's name, Michaela,"},{"time":499572,"text":"and he said, \"Michaela, come up here.\""},{"time":501431,"text":"And she's nine years old, and she was kind of shy,"},{"time":503638,"text":"and she got up there,"},{"time":504999,"text":"and he said, \"Sit down next to me.\""},{"time":507605,"text":"She sat right down next to him."},{"time":509728,"text":"He gave her this big hug, and he said,"},{"time":512536,"text":"\"People ask me why I do this work."},{"time":515788,"text":"I do this work because I'm her dad,"},{"time":518535,"text":"and I don't want anyone ever to hurt her.\""},{"time":522230,"text":"And as a parent, I get it."},{"time":525582,"text":"I get it,"},{"time":527738,"text":"knowing that there are so many sexual assaults"},{"time":530621,"text":"on college campuses"},{"time":532489,"text":"that are so widespread and so under-reported."},{"time":536029,"text":"We've done a lot for adult women."},{"time":538134,"text":"We've got to do a better job for our kids."},{"time":541201,"text":"We just do. We have to. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544391,"text":"We've come a long way"},{"time":546461,"text":"since the days of the Polaroid."},{"time":549472,"text":"Technology has been our friend."},{"time":552625,"text":"The mobile phone is a global game changer"},{"time":556684,"text":"for the empowerment of women,"},{"time":558647,"text":"and Facebook and Twitter and Google and YouTube"},{"time":562852,"text":"and all the social media helps us organize"},{"time":566657,"text":"and tell our story in a powerful way."},{"time":570108,"text":"And so those of you in this audience"},{"time":572606,"text":"who have helped build those applications"},{"time":574447,"text":"and those platforms, as an organizer,"},{"time":576808,"text":"I say, thank you very much."},{"time":579218,"text":"Really. I clap for you."},{"time":581293,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":584274,"text":"I'm the daughter of a man"},{"time":587021,"text":"who joined one club in his life,"},{"time":589292,"text":"the Optimist Club."},{"time":592966,"text":"You can't make that one up."},{"time":595728,"text":"And it is his spirit and his optimism"},{"time":599278,"text":"that is in my DNA."},{"time":601188,"text":"I have been doing this work"},{"time":603050,"text":"for over 30 years,"},{"time":605204,"text":"and I am convinced, now more than ever,"},{"time":607901,"text":"in the capacity of human beings to change."},{"time":611574,"text":"I believe we can bend the arc of human history"},{"time":615113,"text":"toward compassion and equality,"},{"time":618131,"text":"and I also fundamentally believe"},{"time":620949,"text":"and passionately believe"},{"time":622987,"text":"that this violence does not have to be part"},{"time":626117,"text":"of the human condition."},{"time":627942,"text":"And I ask you, stand with us"},{"time":631295,"text":"as we create futures without violence"},{"time":635110,"text":"for women and girls and men and boys everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639530,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641692,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}